name: Wishing Well
description:
Throw your coins to the wishing well and make your wishes! they said your wishes will be come true!

W/A/S/D or Arrow Key to Move your coin and dodge everything! 

You have 2 chance of getting struck until your coin stop moving!

Travel as far as you can! nobody knows what's in the bottom!

(play without fullscreen is the best experience)

music from : patrickdearteaga.com
